                  <h2>Ownership History</h2>
      <p>Leo Castelli Gallery, New York, by 1987. Donald Young Gallery, Chicago, by 1988. Private Collection, Madrid, by 1989. Sold, Donald Young Gallery, to Lannan Foundation, Los Angeles, 1990; fractionally sold and given  to the Art Institute, 1997.</p>
